                        <orgName key="org_112039">Bordesley, Cistercian abbey</orgName>. <origDate when="1210">[c. 1210] (1210). </origDate>. Convention made between W[illiam], the abbot, and convent of Bordesle and Ralph Butler ("Pincerna") of Duresley, concerning the easements which the aforesaid abbot and convent were accustomed to have in the wood of Buddela, viz. that the said Ralph and his heirs shall give to the church of Bordesle 5s. annually for all the said easements, so long as the abbot and convent shall guarantee the same to the said Ralph.</p>
